headline: HiLabs Appoints Robert L. Renzi as Chief Growth Officer to Accelerate Market Expansion and Strategic Partnerships
summary: HiLabs, a leading AI company solving persistent data challenges for U.S. healthcare payers, today announced the appointment of Robert L. Renzi as Chief Growth Officer. With over three decades of leadership experience in healthcare technology, payer solutions, and strategic growth, Rob will lead HiLabs' go-to-market strategy and strengthen its presence across national and regional health plans.
